Name:
MEDIASOUND STOP ID -- stop playing a sound file

Synopsis:
MEDIASOUND STOP ID

Description:
Stop a sound that is playing with the valid identification number Id.

Example:
ID = MEDIASOUND PLAY SoundFile$
sleep 3
MEDIASOUND STOP ID
Explanation:

This first loads the file SoundFile$, plays it for three seconds and then stops it.

Related: mediasound stop